name: podamShouldHandleGenericClassesWithParameterUsedInMultiplePlaces

testSteps.description: When I invoke the factory manufacturing for class uk.co.jemos.podam.test.dto.DefaultMapSingleTypePojo with specific types {class java.lang.String}
Then the pojo uk.co.jemos.podam.test.dto.DefaultMapSingleTypePojo@196b644 must be of the type class uk.co.jemos.podam.test.dto.DefaultMapSingleTypePojo
Then the Map should not be null or empty and each element should have key of type class java.lang.String and value of type class java.lang.String

title: Podam should handle classes with read only maps having same key and value types
